Starten des Mlat Servers:
(mlat_server
_venv) fabian@fabian-Yoga-7-16IAP7:~/Documents/InformatikVault/Semester5/WIPRO/SoftwareServer$ ./mlat-server/mlat-server --work-dir ./mlat-server/workdir --client-listen 0.0.0.0:40147 --status-interval 10


Starten des Mlat Clients:
(mlat_client) fabian@fabian-Yoga-7-16IAP7:~/Documents/InformatikVault/Semester5/WIPRO/SoftwareClient/mlat-client$ mlat-client --input-type beast  --input-connect localhost:30105   --server localhost:40147   --lat 47.1411   --lon 8.4314   --alt 500   --user fabian


Starten von readsb:
(base) fabian@fabian-Yoga-7-16IAP7:~$ readsb   --device-type rtlsdr --net --gain 49.6 --freq 1090000000   --lat 47.1411 --lon 8.4314   --net-bo-port 30105   --modeac   --interactive



