### Commands um RTL SDR Dongle im Docker Container wieder frei zu geben:
Auf Host:
sudo systemctl stop dump1090-fa 2>/dev/null || true
sudo systemctl stop readsb 2>/dev/null || true
sudo systemctl stop rtl_tcp 2>/dev/null || true
sudo pkill -f 'dump1090|readsb|rtl_tcp' 2>/dev/null || true

lsmod | grep -E 'dvb_usb_rtl28xxu|rtl2832'
# If present:
sudo modprobe -r dvb_usb_rtl28xxu rtl2832 2>/dev/null || true



Test im Container selbst:
docker compose exec adsb-processor rtl_test -t

